 408                            headers_[item_.Key] = item_.Value;
 409                        if (response_.Content != null && response_.Content.Headers != null)

 416

 436                        }

 441                            if (objectResponse_.Object == null)

 444                            }
 445                            throw new MistralOCRException<ProblemDetails>("Bad Request", status_, objectResponse_.Text,

 502        protected virtual async System.Threading.Tasks.Task<ObjectResponseResult<T>> ReadObjectResponseAsync<T>(System.N
 503        {
 504            if (response == null || response.Content == null)
 505            {
 506                return new ObjectResponseResult<T>(default(T)!, string.Empty);
 507            }
 508
 509            if (ReadResponseAsString)
 510            {
 511                var responseText = await ReadAsStringAsync(response.Content, cancellation).ConfigureAwait(false);
 512                try
 513                {
 514                    var typedBody = System.Text.Json.JsonSerializer.Deserialize<T>(responseText, JsonSerializerSettings)
 515                    return new ObjectResponseResult<T>(typedBody!, responseText);
 516                }
 517                catch (System.Text.Json.JsonException exception)
 518                {
 519                    var message = "Could not deserialize the response body string as " + typeof(T).FullName + ".";
 520                    throw new MistralOCRException(message, (int)response.StatusCode, responseText, headers, exception);
 521                }
 522            }
 523            else
 524            {
 525                try
 526                {
 527                    using (var responseStream = await ReadAsStreamAsync(response.Content, cancellation).ConfigureAwait(f
 528                    {
 529                        var typedBody = await System.Text.Json.JsonSerializer.DeserializeAsync<T>(responseStream, JsonSe
 530                        return new ObjectResponseResult<T>(typedBody!, string.Empty);
 531                    }
 532                }
 533                catch (System.Text.Json.JsonException exception)
 534                {
 535                    var message = "Could not deserialize the response body stream as " + typeof(T).FullName + ".";
 536                    throw new MistralOCRException(message, (int)response.StatusCode, string.Empty, headers, exception);
 537                }
 538            }
 539        }

 541        private string ConvertToString(object? value, System.Globalization.CultureInfo cultureInfo)
 542        {
 543            if (value == null)
 544            {
 545                return "";
 546            }
 547
 548            if (value is System.Enum)
 549            {
 550                var name = System.Enum.GetName(value.GetType(), value);
 551                if (name != null)
 552                {
 553                    var field = System.Reflection.IntrospectionExtensions.GetTypeInfo(value.GetType()).GetDeclaredField(
 554                    if (field != null)
 555                    {
 556                        var attribute = System.Reflection.CustomAttributeExtensions.GetCustomAttribute(field, typeof(Sys
 557                            as System.Runtime.Serialization.EnumMemberAttribute;
 558                        if (attribute != null)
 559                        {
 560                            return attribute.Value != null ? attribute.Value : name;
 561                        }
 562                    }
 563
 564                    var converted = System.Convert.ToString(System.Convert.ChangeType(value, System.Enum.GetUnderlyingTy
 565                    return converted == null ? string.Empty : converted;
 566                }
 567            }
 568            else if (value is bool)
 569            {
 570                return System.Convert.ToString((bool)value, cultureInfo).ToLowerInvariant();
 571            }
 572            else if (value is byte[])
 573            {
 574                return System.Convert.ToBase64String((byte[]) value);
 575            }
 576            else if (value is string[])
 577            {
 578                return string.Join(",", (string[])value);
 579            }
 580            else if (value.GetType().IsArray)
 581            {
 582                var valueArray = (System.Array)value;
 583                var valueTextArray = new string[valueArray.Length];
 584                for (var i = 0; i < valueArray.Length; i++)
 585                {
 586                    valueTextArray[i] = ConvertToString(valueArray.GetValue(i), cultureInfo);
 587                }
 588                return string.Join(",", valueTextArray);
 589            }
 590
 591            var result = System.Convert.ToString(value, cultureInfo);
 592            return result == null ? "" : result;
 593        }
 594    }
